                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>there; as there are no Israelites<lb/> there worthy of the name,<lb/> &amp; hence\n                Legislation has been<lb/> in accordance to their <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                    >Effati</hi><add>?</add><lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">character</hi>, our indifference<lb/> as a Race to the Laws\n                framed,<lb/> &amp; the <hi rend=\"underline\">general public</hi> welfare,<lb/> are\n                great misfortunes,<lb/> our people only think of<lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">Money &amp; gold</hi>, more the pity<add>?</add><lb/> I am\n                writing that article<lb/> for the Occident.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Yours truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">I Wolf</persName>\n                <add>?</add>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3sj1b747/canvas/p2"
